metadata.name: OMEKA #1
metadata.description:
This is the Gen 1 token of OMEKA

Each of these tokens includes both a new full music track from various artists and a fabulous art piece.

Our ultimate goal is to make listen and earn app for iOS and Android.

You need a gen 1 token to mint gen 2 for free, you can use these tokens to buy music and art from our coming platform and earn our upcoming token.

Read more at www.theomeka.com
